Package: telemon-exporter
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Telemon Maintainers <maintainers@example.invalid>
Description: Native Prometheus exporter for LAN hardware telemetry
 Telemon Exporter exposes Prometheus-compatible metrics for LAN hardware
 monitoring. This package installs the native exporter and systemd service.
